## Root Cause Analysis Summary

**Root Cause**: `ts-seat-service` experiencing HIGH CPU on worker1 (avg 47%, max 115% - exceeding CPU limit), causing extreme node-level resource contention (system load: normal ~24 → abnormal 200-418).

**Fault Propagation**:
1. `ts-seat-service` HIGH CPU → worker1 node overload (system load 8-9x higher)
2. worker1 overload → `ts-food-service` 50% HTTP 500 errors, `ts-travel-plan-service` HIGH_LATENCY, `ts-cancel-service` performance degradation
3. `ts-food-service` errors → `ts-station-food-service` effectively unreachable (1421→5 spans), `ts-ui-dashboard` HIGH_ERROR_RATE
4. `ts-seat-service` slow responses → `ts-travel2-service` HIGH CPU on worker4, cascading to `ts-consign-service`, `ts-assurance-service`, `ts-inside-payment-service`

